dcterms:description: A citation network dataset in high energy physics phenomenology constructed from the e-print arXiv. It covers papers from January 1993 to April 2003.
dcterms:title: HepPh

dcterms:description: A temporal network of interactions on the stack exchange website Math Overflow. A directed edge indicates that user u and user v interacted at time t, including answering questions, commenting questions, and commenting answers.
dcterms:title: MathOverflow

dcterms:description: A temporal network of interactions on the stack exchange website Super User, with the same interaction types as the MathOverflow dataset but on a much larger scale.
dcterms:title: SuperUser
